{"tid":360284,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"果個乜撚頂爺點解呢期成日出黎消費李小龍？","createTime":"2017-08-15T07:27:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T14:49:02.000Z","uid":27939,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a97df8b6be2abec24e72d044e68da62be1a7d90","tid":360284,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T07:27:01.000Z","msg":"如題<br />\n之前個d請一大班嘉賓一路宵夜一路9up果個<br />\n成個節目騎劫左都算<br />\n<br />\n果個乜撚big boys club 仲開足兩集黎講<br />\n講到尾都係消費李小龍<br />\n由頭到尾d問題對佢一d興趣都冇<br />\n<br />\n咁大年紀撈足咁多年<br />\n觀眾對你冇興趣都算，消費個死人黎上位真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n節目間仲好似好撚自豪咁<br />\n究竟要幾厚面皮先做到"},{"pid":"daa8bf469bf22039cae3781bd41f334a2ccdfeab","tid":360284,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T07:47:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8daf5fc811c5f782ab0aafc7754f8ebc8a2adbea","tid":360284,"uid":35841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T07:53:42.000Z","msg":"同乜柒家強一尻樣"},{"pid":"58e0ef980b01b78debb28f10ac57587c2e27551d","tid":360284,"uid":27939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T09:40:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同乜柒家強一尻樣</blockquote><br />\n家強都叫有付出，一齊紅過<br />\n頂爺？冇人識你個老屎忽"},{"pid":"9edd2645203d0d9dce05a02586aee1194884ddbd","tid":360284,"uid":79953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:25:40.000Z","msg":"都唔明佢講為乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為紀念李小龍嘅節目，你講，無問題<br />\n而家你講嚟做乜？為收視？為咗顯示自己幾十年前威威豬？"},{"pid":"50e934b5de94e89bd7cdb3a039fdb655a7f69a45","tid":360284,"uid":102700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:27:27.000Z","msg":"HOCC / 草猛 = 消費梅豔芳"},{"pid":"5ca5bac2d67798772a7f82c537e4e7c4684d0e78","tid":360284,"uid":65144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-15T10:29:42.000Z","msg":"out咁塘都係"},{"pid":"ad06106ca46b587b521f4f3e99e4480